Name: Bee Movie
FilmSynopsis: Barry B. Benson, a bee who has just graduated from college, is disillusioned at his lone career choice: making honey. On a special trip outside the hive, Barry's life is saved by Vanessa, a florist in New York City. As their relationship blossoms, he discovers humans actually eat honey, and subsequently decides to sue us.

Name: Shrek
FilmSynopsis: An ogre, in order to regain his swamp, travels along with an annoying donkey in order to bring a princess to a scheming lord, wishing himself King.

Name: Rush Hour 2
FilmSynopsis: Carter and Lee head to Hong Kong for vacation, but become embroiled in a counterfeit money scam.

Name: Deep Impact
FilmSynopsis: Unless a comet can be destroyed before colliding with Earth, only those allowed into shelters will survive. Which people will survive?

Name: The Long Kiss Goodnight
FilmSynopsis: A women suffering from amnesia begins to recover her memories after trouble from her past finds her again.

Name: Around the World in 80 Days
FilmSynopsis: A bet pits a British inventor, a Chinese thief, and a French artist on a worldwide adventure that they can circle the globe in 80 days.

Name: Mr. and Mrs. Smith
FilmSynopsis: A bored married couple is surprised to learn that they are both assassins hired by competing agencies to kill each other.

Name: Blade
FilmSynopsis: A half-vampire, half-mortal man becomes a protector of the mortal race, while slaying evil vampires.

Name: Collateral
FilmSynopsis: A cab driver finds himself the hostage of an engaging contract killer as he makes his rounds from hit to hit during one night in LA. He must find a way to save both himself and one last victim.

Name: Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon
FilmSynopsis: Two warriors in pursuit of a stolen sword and a notorious fugitive are led to an impetuous, physically-skilled, teenage nobleman's daughter, who is at a crossroads in her life.

Name: Diamonds are Forever
FilmSynopsis: A diamond smuggling investigation leads James Bond to Las Vegas, where he uncovers an extortion plot headed by his nemesis, Ernst Stavro Blofeld.

Name: Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest
FilmSynopsis: Jack Sparrow races to recover the heart of Davy Jones to avoid enslaving his soul to Jones' service, as other friends and foes seek the heart for their own agenda as well.

Name: Armageddon
FilmSynopsis: When an asteroid the size of Texas is headed for Earth the world's best deep core drilling team is sent to nuke the rock from the inside.

Name: Dances With Wolves
FilmSynopsis: Lt. John Dunbar, exiled to a remote western Civil War outpost, befriends wolves and Indians, making him an intolerable aberration in the military.
